<section class="bg-slate-950 text-white py-20 lg:py-24 border-t border-slate-800">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 max-w-6xl">

    <!-- Header -->
    <div class="mb-16 text-center lg:text-left">
      <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-semibold mb-4">
        How we approach growth
      </h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-slate-400 max-w-2xl mx-auto lg:mx-0">
        We don’t start with execution. We start by understanding whether growth
        is financially viable — and only then decide what to build.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Steps -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-12">

      <!-- Step 1 -->
      <div>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 mb-2">
          Phase 1
        </p>
        <h3 class="font-medium text-lg mb-2">
          Clarify the economics
        </h3>
        <p class="text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">
          We assess ticket size, margins, capacity, and constraints to define
          what acquisition can realistically support.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Step 2 -->
      <div>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 mb-2">
          Phase 2
        </p>
        <h3 class="font-medium text-lg mb-2">
          Fix the system
        </h3>
        <p class="text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">
          We identify where demand leaks — messaging, routing, tracking, follow-up —
          and fix those before increasing spend.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Step 3 -->
      <div>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 mb-2">
          Phase 3
        </p>
        <h3 class="font-medium text-lg mb-2">
          Scale with control
        </h3>
        <p class="text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">
          Only after the system works do we introduce scale, testing channels
          and volume without breaking profitability.
        </p>
      </div>

    </div>

    <!-- Ownership note -->
    <div class="mt-16 pt-4 border-t border-slate-800 max-w-xl">
      <a class="text-slate-400 hover:underline hover:text-white transition text-md" href="/process">
        Check How It Works
      </a>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>
